<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link879890" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=879890&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F1338816-how-do-you-think-why-the-book-is-called%2Fanswers%2F879890-yeah-i-guess-it-s">flag</a>
