<span id="freeTextContainer2939875086288534145">Scott Bechtel Smith is an American author and screenwriter. He has published two suspense novels, <u>A Simple Plan</u> and <u>The Ruins</u>, and adapted them for the screen.<br/><br/><i>Librarian Note: There is more than one author in the GoodReads database with this name. <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/topic/show/44217-master-list-of-author-disambiguation-by-spaces' rel='nofollow noopener'>See this thread for more information.</a></i> <br/><br/><i>(from <a href='http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Scott_Smith_(author)' rel='nofollow noopener'>wikipedia</a>)</i></span>
  <span id="freeText2939875086288534145" style="display:none">Scott Bechtel Smith is an American author and screenwriter. He has published two suspense novels, <u>A Simple Plan</u> and <u>The Ruins</u>, and adapted them for the screen.<br /><br /><i>Librarian Note: There is more than one author in the GoodReads database with this name. <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/topic/show/44217-master-list-of-author-disambiguation-by-spaces" rel="nofollow noopener">See this thread for more information.</a></i> <br /><br /><i>(from <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Scott_Smith_(author)" rel="nofollow noopener">wikipedia</a>)</i></span>
